      <title>可可价格飙升，复活节紧缩冲击巧克力货架</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/why-is-easter-candy-expensive-chocolate-egg-prices-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[装满巧克力兔子和柔和色彩的棉花糖的篮子是节日的主食，预计今年复活节美国人将在糖果上花费超过 50 亿美元。但今年，随着可可成本继续飙升，消费者将花更少的钱买更多的钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/why-is-easter-candy-expensive-chocolate-egg-prices-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 14:55:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
